OL,5,Copens
OL,7,FBlackpool's famous rollercoaster, 'The
OL,8,FBig One' ride is not running on the
OL,9,Fopening day of the attraction's season.
OL,11,FThe Pleasure Beach Resort said it had
OL,12,Fa 'sensor malfunction' and the team
OL,13,Fwere working hard to open the ride.
OL,15,FEngineers have spent the closed season
OL,16,Ftesting all the rides, and the UK's
OL,17,Ftallest rollercoaster had been given
OL,18,Fspecial attention after being re-
OL,19,Ftracked and repainted ahead of the
OL,20,Fopening.
