OL,7,FThe first visitors were aware of the
OL,8,Fissue was a series of tweets on X by
OL,9,Fthe resorts CEO, which revealed 'The
OL,10,FBig One' and 'The Ice Blast' would not
OL,11,Fbe running.
OL,13,FThe great-granddaughter of Blackpool
OL,14,FPleasure Beach's founder Amanda
OL,15,FThompson said she was "so sorry" and
OL,16,Fthat it was "beyond my control".
OL,18,FA spokesperson from Pleasure Beach
OL,19,FResort said: "Our teams have been
OL,20,Fworking around the clock to get the
OL,21,Fpark ready for opening.
