OL,7,FThe park said a decision had been made
OL,8,Fnot to run The 'Grand Prix' ride, with
OL,9,Fplans for a new attraction.
OL,11,FWeekend visitors will also be the
OL,12,Ffirst to witness the controversial
OL,13,Frebranding of the iconic attraction.
OL,15,FDespite being known as Blackpool
OL,16,FPleasure Beach for more than 125
OL,17,Fyears, in a bid to move with the
OL,18,Ftimes, it'll be simply called Pleasure
OL,19,FBeach Resort.
